dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Shows the Dnieper River in Ukraine, from Cherkasy to Ochakiv on the Black Sea. "Scala milliarium ad hunc tractum Boristhenis pertinens." German text on verso with caption title: Das Hertzogthumb Litthaw, Samogeten, schwartz Reussen vnd Volhinia; p. 19; signature T. Probably issued in Blaeu's Atlas major (German ed.). Zu Amsterdam : Bey Johannem Blaeu, [ca. 1670].
dct_spatial_sm: Russia. Russian Empire. Soviet Union. Former Soviet Republics
